Class AeExpressionSpecStrategyKey

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers.def.AeSpecStrategyKey
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers.def.AeExpressionSpecStrategyKey
public class AeExpressionSpecStrategyKey
extends AeSpecStrategyKey

An extension of the basic spec strategy key, this version represents a strategy that is dynamically generated by the matcher when the to-spec is a 'expression' form.
